education%20in%20government%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Equal%20and%20quality%20healthcare%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20highlighted%20how%20Delhi%20has%20improved%20government%20hospitals%20and%20opened%20neighborhood%20clinics%2C%20providing%20free%20medication%20and%20medical%20treatment%20to%20all%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Free%20electricity%20for%20all%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20all%20three%20power%20companies%20in%20Delhi%20leading%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20city%20receives%2024%2F7%20electricity%2C%20and%20eligible%20residents%20enjoy%20free%20electricity%2C%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Access%20to%20clean%20water%20for%20all%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20Delhi%20has%20overcome%20water%20scarcity%20in%20many%20areas%20by%20providing%20free%20water%20to%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Respect%20for%20the%20elderly%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20increased%20the%20old-age%20pension%20from%20Rs%201000%20to%20Rs%202500%20and%20initiated%20pilgrimage%20trips%20for%20senior%20citizens%2C%20facilitating%20journeys%20for%2083%2C000%20elderly%20individuals%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Ensuring%20everyone%20feels%20safe%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20his%20speech%2C%20the%20AAP%20leader%20said%20that%20despite%20challenges%20in%20law%20enforcement%2C%20Delhi%20has%20developed%20an%20extensive%20CCTV%20network%2C%20making%20people%20feel%20secure%20and%20aiding%20the%20police%20in%20solving%20major%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Employment%20opportunities%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20has%20created%20jobs%20through%20new%20schools%20and%20neighborhood%20clinics%2C%20and%20a%20job%20portal%20has%20provided%20employment%20to%2010-12%20lakh%20youth%2C%20said%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3