eat%20nation.%20Test%20your%20IQ%20or%20India%20Quotient%20with%20these%2020%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20The%20'Objective%20Resolution'%20moved%20on%2013%20December%2C%201946%20by%20Pandit%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20later%20formed%20the%20basis%20of%20which%20part%20of%20the%20Constitution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20What%20was%20constructed%20in%201724%20by%20Maharaja%20Jai%20Singh%20of%20Jaipur%20because%20he%20found%20the%20existing%20astronomical%20instruments%20too%20small%20to%20take%20correct%20measurements%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Which%20was%20the%20first%20song%20from%20an%20Indian%20film%20to%20win%20an%20Academy%20Award%20for%20Best%20Original%20Song%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20The%20Rs%201000%20currency%20note%20in%20the%20King%20George%20V%20series%20issued%20in%201931%2C%20used%20a%20pictorial%20graphic%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India.%20What%20was%20the%20image%20used%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20On%2023%20August%2C%202023%20which%20organisation%20tweeted%20'India%2C%20I%20reached%20my%20destination%2C%20and%20you%20too!'%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Abhinav%20Brinda%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20hold%20the%20Olympics%20and%20World%20Championships%20title%20simultaneously.%20Who%20is%20the%20second%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20What%20is%20unique%20about%20Karaundi%2C%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Katni%20district%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20Which%20is%20the%20oldest%20regiment%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20raised%20in%201773%20at%20Benares%20by%20the%20then%20Governor%20General%2C%20Warren%20Hastings%2C%20with%20a%20strength%20of%2050%20handpicked%20troopers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20Which%20sweet%20was%20invented%20by%20Kakasura%20Madappa%2C%20the%20royal%20chef%20of%20Maharaja%20Mummadi%20Krishnaraja%20Wadiyar%20in%20the%2019th%20century%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Whose%20doctoral%20thesis%20for%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%20was%20later%20published%20as%20a%20book%20'The%20Problem%20of%20the%20Rupee%3A%20Its%20Origin%20and%20Its%20Solution'%20in%201923%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E11.%20The%20Bharat%20Ratna%20medallion%20is%20shaped%20like%20the%20leaf%20of%20which%20tree%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E12.%20Besides%20the%20need%20for%20strict%20protection%2C%20why%20was%20the%20Bengal%20Tiger%20chosen%20over%20the%20Asiatic%20Lion%20as%20the%20national%20animal%20of%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13.%20The%20first%20fragrant%20stamp%20released%20in%20India%20carried%20the%20fragrance%20of%20what%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E14.%20Started%20formally%20by%20Mahadeo%20Havaji%20Bachche%2C%20which%20service%20was%20awarded%20a%20six%20sigma%20efficiency%20rating%20of%2099.9999%20for%20quality%20assurance%20by%20Forbes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E15.%20Who%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20score%20a%20century%20in%20Pink%20Ball%20test%20cricket%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E16.%20Peaking%20in%20September%2C%20what%20was%20India's%20most%20searched%20'what%20is'%20question%20on%20Google%2C%20in%202023%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E17.%20The%20motifs%20of%20Paithani%20sarees%20are%20derived%20from%20the%20paintings%20of%20which%20Buddhist%20historical%20site%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E18.%20In%20the%20seventh%20century%2C%20the%20first%20written%20evidence%20of%20the%20rules%20for%20working%20with%20what%20were%20formalised%20in%20Brahmagupta's%20book%20Brahmasputha%20Siddhanta%20(The%20Opening%20of%20the%20Universe)%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E19.%20Which%20state%20would%20you%20be%20visiting%20if%20you%20landed%20at%20the%20Lokpriya%20Gopinath%20Bordoloi%20International%20Airport%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E20.%20As%20per%20Geographical%20Indications%20(GI)%20registration%2C%20what%20can%20only%20be%20grown%20in%2087%20gardens%20of%20West%20Bengal%20at%20an%20altitude%20ranging%20from%20610%20to%202134%20metres%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnswers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20The%20Preamble%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Jantar%20Mantar%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Naatu%20Naatu%20from%20the%20film%20RRR%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20A%20farmer%20tilling%20the%20land%20with%20two%20bullocks%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%20The%20full%20tweet%20was%20%26quot%3BChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%20'India%2C%20I%20reached%20my%20destination%20and%20you%20too!'%3A%20Chandrayaan-3.%20Chandrayaan-3%20has%20successfully%20soft-landed%20on%20the%20moon!%20Congratulations%2C%20India!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Neeraj%20Chopra%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20It%20is%20the%20geographical%20centre%20of%20India%20(Pre-partition%2C%20the%20geographical%20centre%20was%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20marked%20by%20the%20Zero%20Mile%20Stone)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20The%20President's%20Bodyguard%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20Mysore%20Pak%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E11.%20Peepal%20leaf%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E12.%20Tiger%20was%20found%20in%20as%20many%20as%2016%20Indian%20states%20whereas%20the%20lion%20was%20only%20found%20in%20one%20state%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E13.%20Sandalwood%20(Released%20in%202006)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E14.%20Mumbai%20Dabbawalas%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E15.%20Smriti%20Mandhana%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E16.%20What%20is%20G20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E17.%20Ajanta%20Caves%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E18.%20Zero%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E19.%20Assam%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E20.%20Darjeeling%20Tea%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScores%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E0-4%3A%20Frankly%2C%20you%20have%20a%20poor%20India%20Quotient%20or%20IQ!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5-8%3A%20Fair%20enough%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9-13%3A%20Very%20well%20done%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E14-20%3A%20You%20can%20write%20an%20encyclopaedia%20on%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EResearch%20credit%3A%20Ayashman%20Dey%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%