rational%20safety.%20The%20Kavach%20system%20helps%20loco%20pilots%20avoid%20signal%20passing%2C%20overspeeding%2C%20and%20improves%20safety%20and%20efficiency%20during%20inclement%20weather%20conditions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fbig-achievement-for-indian-railways-indigenous-kavach-anti-train-collision-system-tested-successfully-at-160-kmph-speed%2Farticleshow%2F107133338.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Billionaire's%20Habit%20of%20Tipping%20Off%20Staff%2C%20Girlfriend%20Lands%20Him%20In%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20edge%20of%20Lago%20Escondido%20in%20Argentina's%20northern%20Patagonia%2C%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20snow-capped%20mountains%2C%20lies%20British%20billionaire%20Joe%20Lewis'%20sprawling%20property.%20He%20frequently%20uses%20the%20luxurious%20estate%20to%20entertain%20public%20officials%20and%20employees%20handpicked%20from%20the%20top%20ranks%20of%20Lewis'%20investment%20firm%20and%20other%20companies%20that%20the%2086-year-old%20has%20an%20interest%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20one%20visit%20in%202006%2C%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20businessmen%20went%20horseback%20riding%20and%20fishing%20and%20admired%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20Picasso's%20Le%20Reve%20and%20two%20versions%20of%20the%20Women%20of%20Algiers%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20Lewis'%20villa%2C%20photos%20obtained%20by%20Bloomberg%20show.%20Trips%20like%20these%2C%20where%20Lewis'%20generosity%20and%20wealth%20are%20on%20display%2C%20are%20partly%20how%20the%20prolific%20investor%20has%20cultivated%20loyalty%20and%20respect%20among%20his%20closest%20advisers%2C%20trusted%20employees%20and%20powerful%20figures%20over%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20more%20than%2015%20years%20after%20that%20Argentina%20jaunt%2C%20Lewis'%20habit%20of%20giving%20lavish%20perks%20to%20employees%20and%20associates%20has%20landed%20him%20in%20legal%20turmoil.%20He%20pleaded%20guilty%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20Manhattan%20Wednesday%20to%20charges%20that%20he%20gave%20his%20longtime%20private%20pilots%20and%20a%20romantic%20partner%20non-public%20inside%20information%20for%20stock%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20possessed%20material%20non%20public%20information%20about%20certain%20publicly%20traded%20companies%2C%20I%20agreed%20to%20make%20recommendations%26quot%3B%20to%20other%20people%20to%20purchase%20stock%2C%20Lewis%20told%20US%20District%20Judge%20Jessica%20Clarke%20at%20a%20hearing.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20at%20the%20time%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20was%20wrong%2C%20and%20I'm%20so%20embarrassed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20deal%20will%20likely%20drastically%20reduce%20any%20sentence%20for%20Lewis%2C%20who%20faced%20as%20long%20as%2045%20years%20in%20prison.%20His%20lawyer%2C%20David%20Zornow%2C%20said%20that%20Lewis%20waived%20his%20right%20to%20appeal%20unless%20he%20is%20sentenced%20to%20jail%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELewis%2C%20who%20was%20indicted%20last%20year%2C%20admitted%20he%20passed%20on%20market-moving%20information%20related%20to%20companies%20he%20invested%20in.%20Unlike%20run%20of%20the%20mill%20insider%20trading%20cases%2C%20Lewis%20didn't%20personally%20reap%20profits%20from%20the%20trades.%20Instead%2C%20prosecutors%20allege%2C%20he%20gave%20information%20to%20his%20pilots%20as%20a%20substitute%20for%20a%20formal%20retirement%20plan%20and%20to%20his%20romantic%20partners%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bshower%26quot%3B%20them%20in%20gifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPilots%20Patrick%20O'Connor%20and%20Bryan%20Waugh%2C%20like%20Lewis%2C%20were%20indicted%20on%20securities%20fraud%20last%20year.%20While%20Lewis'%20former%20girlfriend%2C%20Carolyn%20Carter%2C%20wasn't%20charged%2C%20she%20was%20sued%20by%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%20For%20one%20of%20the%20trades%20cited%20in%20the%20indictment%2C%20Lewis%20allegedly%20loaned%20Waugh%20and%20O'Connor%20%24500%2C000%20apiece%20to%20buy%20shares%20in%20Mirati%20Therapeutics%20Inc.%20before%20news%20of%20the%20company's%20clinical%20trial%20became%20public%20in%202019.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilots%20have%20previously%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20charges%2C%20but%20their%20cases%20are%20scheduled%20for%20a%20hearing%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Flagfbgtk_joe-lewis-bloomberg_625x300_25_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20Lewis%20characterized%20the%20Argentina%20trip%20in%202006%20as%20a%20retreat%20for%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Lewis'%20family%20and%20closest%20colleagues.%26quot%3B%20A%20former%20associate%20who%20has%20been%20to%20the%20estate%20said%20it%20wasn't%20always%20strictly%20a%20family%20affair.%20Employees%20often%20angled%20for%20invites%20to%20such%20trips%2C%20taking%20the%20gesture%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20being%20in%20the%20boss'%20good%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhotos%20from%20the%20trip%20show%20Lewis%20triumphantly%20displaying%20his%20catch%20and%20leading%20colleagues%20on%20horseback%20through%20streams%20near%20his%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Ritz%20Carlton%20on%20the%20Water'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELewis%2C%20who%20is%20now%20worth%20about%20%247.6%20billion%20according%20to%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index%2C%20dropped%20out%20of%20high%20school%20to%20work%20at%20his%20father's%20London%20catering%20business.%20He%20eventually%20built%20that%20operation%20into%20a%20chain%20of%20themed%20restaurants%2C%20then%20sold%20it%20and%20used%20the%20profits%20to%20reinvent%20himself%20as%20a%20currency%20trader.%20He%20relocated%20to%20the%20uber-rich%20Bahamas%20hamlet%20of%20Lyford%20Cay%20to%20avoid%20UK%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20financial%20lore%2C%20his%20first%20big%20score%20was%20betting%20against%20the%20British%20pound%20in%201992.%20That%20was%20the%20same%20trade%20that%20netted%20George%20Soros%20%241%20billion%2C%20though%20Lewis's%20take%20was%20probably%20much%20smaller%2C%20according%20to%20traders.%20He%20landed%20another%20big%20win%20investing%20in%20Russian%20energy%20giant%20Gazprom%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20according%20to%20two%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20much%20of%20his%20success%20since%20then%20has%20been%20tied%20to%20Tavistock%20Group%2C%20a%20holding%20company%20that%20has%20stakes%20in%20more%20than%20200%20businesses%20worldwide%2C%20including%20the%20five-star%20St.%20Regis%20hotel%20in%20Atlanta%20and%20the%20Isleworth%20Golf%20Club%20in%20Florida.%20Lewis%20also%20owns%20Albany%2C%20an%20exclusive%20gated%20community%20in%20Nassau%20in%20the%20Bahamas%20where%20he%20was%20occasionally%20spotted%20playing%20padel%20tennis%20with%20penthouse%20resident%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20before%20the%20FTX%20co-founder's%202022%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20his%20wealth%20is%20now%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20developing%20Lake%20Nona%2C%20an%20exclusive%20community%20near%20Orlando%2C%20Florida%2C%20and%20a%20luxury%20equestrian%20community%20in%20Palm%20Beach%20County%20with%20celebrity%20Justin%20Timberlake%20and%20golfer%20Tiger%20Woods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELewis%2C%20through%20a%20family%20trust%20and%20his%20California-based%20biotech%20fund%20Boxer%20Capital%2C%20holds%20stakes%20in%20three%20companies%20that%20are%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20insider%20trading%20charges%20against%20him%2C%20including%20Australian%20Agricultural%20Co.%20and%20Mirati%20Therapeutics.%20The%20companies%20weren't%20accused%20of%20any%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Lewis%20yacht%2C%20Aviva%2C%20in%20London.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Joe%20Lewis%20yacht%2C%20Aviva%2C%20in%20London.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6p1lgaug_joe-lewis-yacht-aviva-london-bloomberg_625x300_25_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Lewis'%20yacht%2C%20Aviva%2C%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELewis%2C%20who%20also%20used%20to%20own%20the%20Premier%20League%20football%20club%20Tottenham%20Hotspur%2C%20is%20notoriously%20private%20and%20rarely%20talks%20to%20the%20press.%20He%20prefers%20to%20do%20business%20on%20his%20superyacht%2C%20Aviva%2C%20where%20he%20was%20often%20able%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20public%20eye.%20Years%20ago%2C%20he'd%20sail%20to%20the%20Mediterranean%20for%20the%20summer%20and%20party%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20late%20Australian%20media%20mogul%20Kerry%20Packer%20but%20still%20managed%20to%20call%20traders%20collect%20from%20the%20ship%20when%20it%20was%20time%20to%20work%2C%20two%20people%20familiar%20with%20his%20social%20circle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20322-foot%20boat%20%E2%80%94%20which%20one%20former%20colleague%20described%20as%20%26quot%3BRitz%20Carlton%20on%20the%20water%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Lewis%20has%20been%20known%20to%20invite%20board%20members%20on%20deck%20for%20meetings%20when%20it's%20moored%20in%20New%20York's%20East%20River%20or%20a%20port%20in%20California.%20The%20boat%20has%20its%20own%20padel%20tennis%20court%20below%20deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202019%2C%20Lewis%20invited%20a%20Boxer%20Capital%20employee%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20also%20on%20Mirati%20Therapeutics's%20board%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20visit%20on%20the%20Aviva%20in%20California.%20During%20his%20weeklong%20stay%2C%20the%20employee%20shared%20information%20about%20Mirati's%20clinical%20trial%20results%20and%20upcoming%20corporate%20announcements%2C%20predicting%20that%20the%20share%20p