y%20way%20to%20blow%20up%20the%20plane%20(I'm%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Taliban).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma%20told%20a%20Madrid%20court%20on%20Monday%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20intention%20was%20never%20to%20cause%20public%20distress%20or%20cause%20public%20harm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20found%20guilty%2C%20the%20student%20could%20be%20facing%20substantial%20expenses%2C%20as%20two%20Spanish%20Air%20Force%20jets%20were%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20detection%20by%20UK%20security%20services%2C%20Mr%20Verma's%20message%20was%20promptly%20brought%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20Spanish%20authorities%20while%20the%20easyJet%20plane%20was%20still%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20proceedings%20in%20a%20Madrid%20court%2C%20it%20was%20assumed%20that%20the%20message%20raised%20concerns%20after%20being%20intercepted%20through%20Gatwick's%20Wi-Fi%20network.%20Subsequently%2C%20two%20Spanish%20F-18%20fighter%20jets%20were%20sent%20to%20flank%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20jets%20closely%20trailed%20the%20plane%20until%20it%20touched%20down%20in%20Menorca%2C%20where%20an%20extensive%20search%20was%20conducted.%20Mr%20Verma%2C%20who%20was%2018%20at%20the%20time%2C%20was%20arrested%20and%20spent%20two%20days%20in%20police%20custody%20before%20being%20released%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20returning%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20he%20underwent%20questioning%20by%20British%20intelligence%20agencies%20MI5%20and%20MI6%20before%20heading%20back%20to%20his%20home%20in%20Orpington%2C%20Kent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20in%20court%20on%20Monday%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20-%20who%20is%20now%20studying%20economics%20at%20Bath%20University%20-%20said%20the%20message%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20joke%20in%20a%20private%20group%20setting%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20sent%20to%20my%20friends%20I%20was%20travelling%20with%20on%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%