%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20that%20Bopanna%20has%20entered%20the%20Australian%20Open%20final.%20In%20the%20last%20Grand%20Slam%20he%20played%20(US%20Open%202023)%2C%20Bopanna%20and%20Ebden%20had%20entered%20the%20final%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20seeded%20Indo-Australian%20pair%20faced%20some%20stiff%20resistance%20from%20their%20rivals%20in%20the%20third%20set%20but%20eventually%20the%20experience%20of%20playing%20Super%20Tie%20Breakers%20helped%20them%20nail%20the%20finish%20with%20a%206-3%203-6%207-6%20(10-7)%20scoreline%20after%20two%20hours%20and%20two%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20he%20was%20assured%20of%20becoming%20the%20world%20number%20one%20player%2C%20Bopanna%20as%20usual%20served%20well%20on%20big%20points%20and%20also%20manage%20to%20pull%20out%20the%20strokes%20and%20tricks%20when%20they%20needed%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBopanna%20has%20reached%20the%20US%20Open%20final%20twice%20(2013%2C%202023)%20but%20a%20Major%20trophy%20has%20eluded%20him%20in%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20at%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20his%20career%20at%20the%20age%20of%2043%2C%20he%20will%20have%20the%20chance%20to%20tick%20that%20box%20on%20Saturday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Bopanna%20due%20to%20his%20exceptional%20form%2C%20secured%20the%20World%20No.%201%20spot%20in%20men's%20doubles%20tennis.%20Pairing%20with%20Matthew%20Ebden%2C%20the%2043-year-old%20has%20reached%20the%20semi-finals%20of%20the%20Australian%20Open%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20his%20prolonged%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Sony%20Sports%20Network%2C%20Bopanna%20said%20that%20after%20being%20there%20in%20the%20sport%2C%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20amazing.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20Indian%20tennis%20needed%20this%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20absolutely%20amazing%20and%20incredible%20to%20be%20where%20I%20am%20today%2C%20especially%20after%202