ID).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20police%20chief%20GP%20Singh%20has%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20the%20case%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20the%20CID%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bthorough%20and%20in-depth%20investigation%20through%20a%20SIT%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20other%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20nine%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20including%20those%20related%20to%20rioting%2C%20unlawful%20assembly%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20workers%20part%20of%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20Yatra%20clashed%20with%20Assam%20cops%20this%20Tuesday%20near%20the%20Guwahati%20city%20limits.%20The%20state%20BJP%20government%20had%20barred%20the%20yatra%20from%20moving%20on%20key%20Guwahati%20roads%2C%20citing%20the%20possibility%20of%20traffic%20jams.%20Declaring%20the%20grounds%20of%20denying%20permission%20frivolous%2C%20Congress%20workers%20tried%20to%20enter%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20contingent%20of%20cops%20had%20been%20posted%20at%20the%20city%20borders%20to%20stop%20them.%20About%205%2C000%20Congress%20workers%20clashed%20with%20them%2C%20leading%20to%20chaotic%20scenes%20at%20the%20city%20limits.%20Mr%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Sarma%20alleged%20that%20Congress's%20%26quot%3Bnaxalite%20tactics%26quot%3B%20led%20to%20a%20massive%20traffic%20jam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20swift%20transfer%20of%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CID%20comes%20amid%20a%20heated%20exchange%20between%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20Mr%20Sarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20was%20creating%20one%20hurdle%20after%20another%20in%20the%20yatra.%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20written%20to%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20flagging%20incidents%20of%20breach%20in%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20security%20ever%20since%20his%20yatra%20entered%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20public%20addresses%20in%20Assam%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20slammed%20Mr%20Sarma%20for%20being%20the%20country's%20most%20corrupt%20Chief%20Minister.%20He%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20remote-controlled%20by%20the%20centre%20from%20Delhi.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20dared%20the%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20register%20more%20case%20against%20him%20and%20said%20he%20is%20not%20scared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20MP%20of%20instigating%20people%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20trying%20to%20destablise%20Assam.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20arrest%20him%20(Rahul)%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20If%20we%20arrest%20him%20before%2C%20it%20will%20become%20politicised.%20Now%20the%20case%20has%20been%20registered%2C%20SIT%20will%20investigate%2C%20and%20we%20have%20evidence.%20A%20big%20incident%20could%20have%20happened%20in%20Guwahati%20after%20he%20instigated%20to%20break%20barricades.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20politics%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20because%20we%20are%20going%20to%20win%20this%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20is%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra's%20last%20day%20in%20Assam%2C%20after%20which%20it%20will%20enter%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706157360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F1ihsmsd8_assam-police_625x300_25_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-himanta-sarma-assam-case-against-rahul-gandhi-transferred-to-cid-amid-row-over-yatra-4927737%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20case%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20associates%20in%20connection%20with%20Congress%20leaders'%20clash%20with%20cops%20at%20Guwahati%20city%20limits%20will%20now%20be%20investigated%20by%20the%20specialised%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%20(CID).%22%2C