2Fstrong%3EIn%20all%20her%2019%20years%20with%20Target%2C%20she%20said%20she'd%20%26quot%3Bnever%20been%20written%20up%2C%20never%20called%20out%2C%20never%20been%20late.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20January%203%2C%20she%20stopped%20by%20her%20store's%20Starbucks%20caf%C3%A9%20while%20on%20break%2C%20where%20she%20said%20a%20barista%20asked%20her%20if%20she%20wanted%20to%20buy%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchaos-stampede-limited-edition-stanley-cups-target-vday-resale-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexclusive%20Starbucks%20x%20Stanley%20mugs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mama%20passed%20from%20breast%20cancer%2C%20so%20I%20always%20try%20to%20get%20as%20much%20pink%20as%20I%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20managers%20were%20present%20during%20the%20transaction%20and%20raised%20no%20objection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20terminated%20the%20following%20week%20thanks%20to%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchaos-stampede-limited-edition-stanley-cups-target-vday-resale-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epink%20stainless%20steel%20insulated%20cup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20retailed%20for%20%2449.95.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarter%20is%20one%20of%20many%20workers%20across%20the%20US%20that%20Target%20has%20fired%20this%20month%20after%20they%20purchased%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstanley-cup-trend-gen-z-peaked-what-is-next-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especial-edition%20Stanley%20Quencher%20mugs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeven%20workers%20told%20BI%20store%20leaders%2C%20including%20human%20resources%20and%20asset%20protection%20representatives%2C%20cited%20a%20company%20policy%20that%20prohibits%20employees%20from%20using%20their%20position%20to%20%26quot%3Bgain%20an%20unfair%20advantage%20over%20guests%26quot%3B%20in%20order%20to%20purchase%20merchandise.%20All%20of%20the%20employees'%20identities%20and%20employments%20were%20verified%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20especially%20concerns%20high-demand%20or%20limited-stock%20items%20and%20deals%2C%20such%20as%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20trading%20cards%20and%20PlayStation%20consoles.%20None%20of%20the%20seven%20workers%20could%20recall%20a%20situation%20in%20which%20a%20peer%20in%20their%20store%20was%20terminated%20for%20violating%20the%20employee%20purchase%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20said%20they%20offered%20to%20return%20the%20cup%20when%20they%20were%20informed%20of%20the%20problem.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETheir%20offers%20were%20declined.%20Almost%20all%20the%20workers%20said%20their%20store%20leaders%20indicated%20that%20the%20investigations%20were%20directed%20by%20Target's%20corporate%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20multiple%20requests%20for%20comment%20last%20week%20or%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20retailers%2C%20Target%20is%20an%20at-will%20employer%2C%20which%20means%20it%20may%20terminate%20a%20worker's%20employment%20at%20any%20time%20for%20any%20reason%2C%20or%20for%20no%20reason%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20anecdotes%20on%20social%20media%20indicate%20cases%20of%20flagrant%20violations%20of%20the%20policy.%20But%20workers%20BI%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20they%20were%20either%20unaware%20of%20the%20rule's%20existence%20or%20that%20they%20did%20not%20realize%20they%20violated%20the%20rule%20when%20they%20purchased%20one%20of%20the%20cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20two%20cases%2C%20workers%20told%20BI%20they%20bought%20a%20cup%20that%20was%20improperly%20set%20aside%20by%20a%20colleague.%20In%20two%20others%2C%20workers%20bought%20cups%20that%20hadn't%20been%20properly%20%26quot%3Bre-shopped%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20returned%20to%20the%20correct%20location%20on%20the%20sales%20floor%20%E2%80%94%20after%20online%20orders%20were%20cancelled.%20Two%2C%20including%20Carter%2C%20said%20their%20managers%20either%20witnessed%20or%20otherwise%20expressly%20approved%20their%20purchases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Starbucks%20team%20lead%20in%20Maryland%20never%20even%20bought%20a%20cup%2C%20but%20told%20BI%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshe%20was%20terminated%20Wednesday%20for%20allowing%20one%20to%20be%20sold%20before%20the%20official%20release%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20store's%20standard%20practice%20was%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20stock%20items%20ahead%20of%20schedule%20when%20other%20seasonal%20merchandise%20had%20sold%20out%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20displaying%20empty%20shelves.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20all%20of%20the%20holiday%20merchandise%20had%20sold%2C%20so%20she%20said%20her%20manager%20directed%20her%20to%20set%20out%20the%20Stanleys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20another%20Starbucks%20cup.%20I%20don't%20need%20a%20Stanley.%20I%20don't%20need%20any%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20allowed%20one%20of%20my%20team%20members%20to%20buy%20a%20cup%20because%20he%20was%20my%20team%20member%20and%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20people%20who%20was%20consistently%20closing%20with%20me.%20When%20we'd%20have%20call-outs%20I%20could%20count%20on%20him%20to%20come%20in%20and%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20each%20worker%20told%20BI%20they%20were%20one%20of%20several%20employees%20at%20their%20stores%20who%20had%20been%20fired%20over%20the%20cups.%20Four%20said%20they%20knew%20of%20multiple%20workers%20at%20other%20stores%20in%20their%20district%20losing%20their%20jobs.%20Target%20has%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.target.com%2Fabout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2%2C000%20stores%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20employs%20over%20400%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20dozen%20other%20individuals%20shared%20similar%20experiences%2C%20though%20BI%20was%20unable%20to%20verify%20each%20of%20those%20in%20time%20for%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20