%20personal%20experience%20or%20related%20story.%20A%20Maintainer%20will%20affirm%20what's%20being%20said%20or%20ask%20more%20specific%20questions%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMagee%20said%20that%20these%20categories%20have%20helped%20her%20better%20understand%20%E2%80%94%20and%20salvage%20%E2%80%94%20her%20friendships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spent%20many%20years%20cutting%20off%20relationships%20with%20people%20who%20had%20the%20opposite%20style%20because%20I%20would%20become%20so%20resentful%20and%20frustrated%20in%20my%20connection%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Magee%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20have%20the%20tools%20or%20the%20framework%20to%20talk%20about%20it%20with%20them%2C%20so%20I%20would%20just%20be%20in%20the%20situation%20feeling%20unseen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMagee%20had%20communication%20problems%20with%20two%20of%20her%20own%20friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hailey%20Magee%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b189bc6c8f0a134f79d1cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHailey%20Magee.%3Cp%3EErek%20West%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMagee%2C%20who%20identifies%20as%20an%20Invite-Only%20and%20Maintainer%2C%20said%20she%20was%20partly%20inspired%20to%20discuss%20the%20different%20types%20of%20communication%20styles%20after%20she%20ran%20into%20the%20same%20miscommunication%20issue%20with%20two%20different%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20always%20the%20one%20asking%20questions%20and%20diving%20deep%20into%20what%20my%20friends%20were%20saying%2C%26quot%3B%20Magee%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20felt%20like%20very%20few%20people%20were%20offering%20me%20the%20same%20curiosity%20or%20attentiveness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20Magee%20specializes%20in%20helping%20her%20clients%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-stop-being-a-people-pleaser-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estop%20people-pleasing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20felt%20she%20had%20to%20try%20talking%20to%20her%20friends%20rather%20than%20keep%20stewing.%20So%20she%20spoke%20to%20each%20one%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20nerve-racking%2C%20but%20it%20was%20such%20an%20eye-opening%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20While%20she%20saw%20her%20friends%20as%20self-centered%20and%20uncurious%2C%20they%20each%20told%20her%20she%20came%20off%20as%20closed-off%20and%20guarded%20because%20she%20never%20shared%20anything%20about%20herself%20and%20just%20kept%20asking%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMagee%20said%20that%20the%20labels%20not%20only%20helped%20her%20express%20what%20she%20needed%20and%20gave%20her%20friends%20a%20chance%20to%20adjust%2C%20but%20they%20also%20gave%20her%20a%20more%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20how%20communication%20differs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20get%20frustrated%20with%20people%20not%20because%20they've%20communicated%20in%20a%20way%20that's%20objectively%20bad%20or%20wrong%2C%20but%20because%20we've%20made%20meaning%20out%20of%20how%20they%20communicate%2C%26quot%3B%20Magee%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20meaning%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere's%20no%20perfect%20type%20of%20communication%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMagee%20said%20that%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20pros%20and%20cons%26quot%3B%20for%20every%20communication%20type.%20For%20example%2C%20Maintainers%20might%20think%20Builders%20hijack%20conversations%20and%20make%20it%20all%20about%20them%2C%20while%20Builders%20can%20view%20Maintainers%20as%20cold%20and%20distant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20things%20trickier%20is%20that%20these%20personality%20types%20can%20often%20attract%20each%20other%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20they%20also%20grate%20against%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20my%20comments%20section%20is%20any%20indication%2C%20it%20really%20does%20seem%20like%20Volunteers%20and%20Invite-Onlies%20tend%20to%20find%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Magee%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20one%20person%20tends%20more%20toward%20listening%2C%20the%20other%20tends%20more%20toward%20speaking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20there's%20no%20%26quot%3Bbad%26quot%3B%20communication%20style%2C%20Magee%20said%20extremes%20on%20either%20side%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20deal%20with.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20personally%20feel%20like%20those%20of%20us%20who%20veer%20really%20strongly%20in%20one%20direction%20in%20any%20of%20these%20pairs%20would%20probably%20benefit%20from%20experimenting%20with%20what%20it%20would%20be%20like%20to%20maybe%20bring%20the%20pendulum%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20center%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELabels%20can%20help%20you%20name%20your%20needs%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMagee%20said%20the%20goal%20of%20these%20labels%20isn't%20to%20pressure%20people%20to%20change%20or%20only%20find%20people%20with%20the%20same%20types%2C%20but%20to%20use%20them%20as%20tools%20to%20share%20how%20you%20feel%20when%20your%20needs%20aren't%20being%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20silently%20holding%20these%20needs%20and%20then%20resentments%20when%20they're%20not%20met%2C%20the%20solution%20is%20to%20open%20the%20dialogue%20with%20the%20people%20close%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Magee%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20still%20talks%20to%20her%20Volunteer%20friends%20when%20she%20feels%20overlooked%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20conversations%20help%20reassure%20her%20that%20they%20value%20the%20friendship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20she%20said%2C%20our%20communication%20types%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20who%20we're%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20around%20other%20Invite-Onlies%2C%20funnily%20enough%2C%20I%20step%20more%20into%20Volunteer%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20Magee%20said.%20When%20her%20friends%20adjust%20to%20ask%20her%20more%20questions%2C%20she%20feels%20more%20comfortable%20sharing%20about%20herself%2C%20completely%20unprompted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftypes-of-communication-styles-improve-friendship-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706140178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b1a1ee43bb77284ba06b37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftypes-of-communication-styles-improve-friendship-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%206%20communication%20styles%2C%20life%20coach%20Hailey%20Magee%20says.%20Understanding%20each%20type%20will%20improve%20your%20friendships%20and%20romantic%20relationships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftypes-of-communication-styles-improve-friendship-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turkiye%20backs%20Sweden's%20Nato%20bid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706140025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107127207%2Cimgsize-1171764.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fturkiyes-parliament-approves-swedens-nato-bid-latest-news%2Farticleshow%2F107127193.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107127193.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETurkiye's%20parliament%20voted%20Tuesday%20to%20allow%20Sweden%20to%20join%20Nato%2C%20putting%20the%20Nordic%20country%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20entering%20the%20military%20alliance%20and%20easing%20a%20diplomatic%20stalemate%20that%20has%20clouded%20Turkiye's%20relations%20with%20the%20US%20