C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eincluding%20the%20SAG-AFTRA%20strike%20and%20its%20Christmas%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLate-breaking%20releases%20are%20no%20longer%20the%20favorites%20in%20the%20Oscar%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20Boelman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20even%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20the%20traditional%20wisdom%20was%20that%20a%20film%20had%20to%20come%20out%20in%20November%2C%20December%2C%20to%20really%20be%20an%20'awards%20movie.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoelman%20pointed%20out%20that%20many%20of%20the%20recent%20best%20picture%20winners%20came%20out%20in%20spring%20and%20summer%20instead%20of%20late%20fall%20or%20winter.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2022's%20winner%2C%20%26quot%3BCoda%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20an%20August%20release%2C%20while%20last%20year's%20best%20picture%2C%20%26quot%3BEverything%20Everywhere%20All%20at%20Once%2C%26quot%3B%20premiered%20in%20March.%20Even%20the%202024%20frontrunner%2C%20%26quot%3BOppenheimer%2C%26quot%3B%20famously%20hit%20theaters%20alongside%20fellow%20best%20picture%20nominee%20%26quot%3BBarbie%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbie-oppenheimer-same-release-date-reason-christopher-nolan-superstitious-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20July%2021.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20waiting%20until%20December%20to%20release%20'The%20Color%20Purple%2C'%20they%20were%20late%20to%20the%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20'The%20Color%20Purple'%20that%20suffered%20from%20that.%20The%20other%20movie%20that%20really%20suffered%20from%20that%20I%20would%20think%20is%20'The%20Iron%20Claw.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20strike%20going%20from%20July%20to%20November%209%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Color%20Purple%26quot%3B%20cast%20couldn't%20promote%20the%20movie%20until%20about%20a%20month%20out%20from%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20was%20a%20mad%20dash%20to%20try%20to%20watch%20every%20winter%20title%20under%20the%20sun%20in%20a%20short%20time%2C%20which%20also%20likely%20hurt%20titles%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BThe%20Color%20Purple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20late%20releases%20like%20%26quot%3BPoor%20Things%26quot%3B%20(December%208)%20and%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20Fiction%26quot%3B%20(December%2015)%20received%20Oscar%20love%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20Us%20Strangers%26quot%3B%20(December%2022)%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw%26quot%3B%20(December%2022)%2C%20%26quot%3BFerrari%26quot%3B%20(December%2025)%2C%20%26quot%3BOrigin%26quot%3B%20(which%20had%20a%20one-week%20release%20in%20December%20for%20eligibility)%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Color%20Purple%26quot%3B%20were%20largely%20shut%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Posters%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BOrigin%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20Us%20Strangers%26quot%3B%20side%20by%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b1708343bb77284ba04e54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Iron%20Claw%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BOrigin%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20Us%20Strangers%26quot%3B%20all%20received%20zero%20Academy%20Award%20nominations.%20Andrew%20Scott%20was%20nominated%20for%20best%20actor%20at%20the%20Golden%20Globes%20for%20his%20lead%20role%20in%20the%20latter%20film.%3Cp%3EA24%3B%20Neon%3B%20Searchlight%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNormally%2C%20we're%20getting%20screeners%20in%20the%20mail%20around%20the%20end%20of%20October%2C%20beginning%20of%20November%2C%20but%20this%20year%20we%20didn't%20start%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20screeners%20in%20the%20mail%20until%20right%20before%20Thanksgiving%2C%26quot%3B%20Boelman%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20voters%20might%20not%20have%20had%20the%20time%20to%20really%20see%20the%20movie%20before%20the%20voting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they're%20waiting%20until%20later%20to%20screen%20it%20and%20everybody's%20trying%20to%20cram%20in%20everything%20they%20can%20watch%20in%20that%20short%20period%20of%20time%2C%20some%20things%20are%20going%20to%20get%20left%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20may%20be%20one%20reason%20both%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fartisans%2Fnews%2Fcostume-designers-guild-nominations-2024-1235860936%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECostume%20Designers%20Guild%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpse.org%2Fpage-18226%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMotion%20Picture%20Sound%20Editors%3C%2Fa%3E%20shut%20out%20%26quot%3BThe%20Color%20Purple%26quot%3B%20when%20their%20nominations%20were%20announced%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20recognition%20could've%20given%20vital%20support%20in%20the%20Oscar%20race%2C%20where%20%26quot%3BThe%20Color%20Purple%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20bold%2C%20bright%20dresses%20and%20pants%20should've%20been%20a%20shoo-in%20for%20best%20costume%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fantasia%20Barrino%20and%20Taraji%20P.%20Henson%20perform%20%26quot%3BWhat%20About%20Love%3F%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Color%20Purple.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6580895150edbc52a8654d9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFantasia%20Barrino%20and%20Taraji%20P.%20Henson%20perform%20%26quot%3BWhat%20About%20Love%3F%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Color%20Purple.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEli%20Ade%C2%B4%2FWarner%20Bros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20guilds%20are%20normally%20awards%20that%20musicals%20do%20very%2C%20very%20well%20in%2C%20and%20for%20the%20film%20to%20have%20not%20shown%20up%20in%20either%20of%20those%20awards%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20movie%20was%20on%20its%20wa