0%94%20have%20had%20real%20trouble%20keeping%20eyeballs%2C%20giving%20the%20competing%20lure%20of%20TikTok%20or%20YouTube%20or%20whatever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Stewart%20left%20%26quot%3BThe%20Daily%20Show%26quot%3B%20in%202015%2C%20he%20was%20bringing%20in%20an%20average%20of%202.2%20million%20viewers%20a%20night%2C%20according%20to%20Nielsen.%20By%20the%20time%20his%20replacement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrevor-noah-exiting-daily-show-after-7-years-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrevor%20Noah%20signed%20off%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20number%20had%20shrunk%20to%20600%2C000.%20And%20during%202023%2C%20when%20Comedy%20Central%20used%20a%20battery%20of%20guest%20hosts%20to%20keep%20the%20show%20going%2C%20that%20audience%20had%20shrunk%20to%20570%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertisers%20are%20very%20aware%20of%20the%20decay%3A%20Between%202018%20and%202022%2C%20late-night%20ad%20dollars%20dropped%20by%2040%25%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Flate-night-tv-ratings-horror-story-colbert-fallon-kimmel-1235583880%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVariety%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20maybe%20wondering%20about%20Stewart's%20TV%20audience%20isn't%20the%20right%20question.%20After%20Stewart's%20news%20broke%2C%20I%20made%20a%20couple%20calls%20to%20people%20who%20have%20a%20good%20bead%20on%20late%20night%20and%20Stewart%20and%20they%20told%20me%20to%20view%20it%20this%20way%3A%20Ignore%20the%20TV%20ratings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20concentrate%20on%20the%20way%20clips%20from%20Stewart's%20weekly%20show%20perform%20on%20social%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20likes%20of%20TikTok%20or%20YouTube%20or%20whatever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20%3Cem%3Ekind%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eof%3C%2Fem%3E%20obvious%20advice%20in%202024%2C%20when%20late-night%20comedy%20is%20routinely%20cut%20up%20and%20distributed%20on%20the%20internet.%20But%20also%20not%20completely%20obvious.%20If%20TV%20ratings%20aren't%20important%2C%20then%20why%20would%20Stewart%20come%20back%20to%20a%20TV%20network%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20would%20a%20TV%20network%20care%20about%20landing%20Stewart%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Stewart%2C%20who%20spent%20the%20past%20few%20years%20toiling%20in%20near%20obscurity%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F19%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia%2Fjon-stewart-the-problem-ends.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20TV%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20(if%20you%20haven't%20seen%20it%2C%20you're%20not%20alone)%2C%20it%20can%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20getting%20back%20in%20the%20public%20eye.%20Doing%20a%20thing%20he's%20good%20at%20on%20Comedy%20Central%20%E2%80%94%20the%20thing%20he%20was%20good%20at%20doing%20on%20Comedy%20Central%20a%20decade%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20a%20real%20boost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20about%20getting%20a%20platform%20that%20can%20then%20get%20social%20currency%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20TV%20insider%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BHe%20needs%20a%20home%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20Stewart%20doesn't%20need%20Comedy%20Central%20to%20host%20and%20produce%20a%20TV%20show%2C%20then%20get%20clips%20from%20those%20shows%20cut%20up%20and%20distributed%20to%20various%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20could%20finance%20all%20of%20that%20himself%2C%20or%20find%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20put%20up%20the%20money.%20My%20TikTok%20is%20full%20of%20people%20self-producing%20%26quot%3BDaily%20Show%26quot%3B-style%20comedy%20and%20interviews%20(with%20very%20varied%20results).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%3A%20Coming%20back%20to%20Comedy%20Central%20means%20he'll%20have%20a%20turnkey%20operation%20that%20knows%20how%20to%20make%20TV%20and%20has%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20money%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20make%20bits%20of%20TV%20travel%20on%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20performer%2C%20and%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20TV%20watcher%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%2C%20old%20people%20like%20me%20%E2%80%94%20a%20brand%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Daily%20Show%26quot%3B%20still%20has%20meaning%20and%20resonance%2C%20even%20when%20it%20gets%20cut%20up%20and%20clipped%20on%20Instagram%20or%20whatever.%20It's%20going%20to%20garner%20attention%20in%20a%20way%20that%20Jon%20Stewart%20Talks%20On%20YouTube%20would%20struggle%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20make%20no%20mistake%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Daily%20Show%26quot%3B%20audience%20was%20old%20when%20Stewart%20was%20on%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20the%20median%20age%20of%20his%20viewers%20was%2048%20when%20he%20left%20the%20show%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20has%20gotten%20much%2C%20much%20older%3A%20Nielsen%20says%20the%20show's%20median%20viewer%20age%20was%2060%20during%20Noah's%20last%20year%2C%20and%20more%20than%2063%20during%20the%202023%20guest%20host%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20from%20Comedy%20Central's%20perspective%3F%20They%20are%2C%20after%20all%2C%20a%20cable%20TV%20network%20owned%20by%20a%20TV%20company%20that%20primarily%20gets%20paid%20when%20people%20subscribe%20to%20their%20networks%20or%20watch%20their%20shows%20on%20TV.%20It's%20not%20easy%20to%20make%20real%20money%20from%20YouTube%20clips%2C%20and%20next%20to%20impossible%20(right%20now)%20from%20TikTok%20or%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20theory%20is%20that%20Stewart's%20old%20audience%2C%20who%20are%20%E2%80%A6%20old%2C%20will%20indeed%20come%20back%20to%20watch%20him.%20That%20audience%20is%20still%20buoying%20Stewart%20protege%20Stephen%20Colbert%20at%20CBS%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fstephen-colbert-jimmy-kimmel-fall-late-night-talk-show-ratings-1235841487%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Late%20Show%26quot%3B%20averages%20a%20bit%20under%202%20million%20viewers%20a%20night%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20if%20they%20don't%2C%20the%20TV%20people%20