pect%20India%20to%20treat%20British%20citizens%20fairly%20at%20all%20times%20in%20its%20visa%20process.%20We%20have%20previously%20raised%20the%20issues%20British%20citizens%20with%20Pakistani%20heritage%20experience%20applying%20for%20visas%20with%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20London.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBashir%2C%20a%20Surrey-born%20British%20passport%20holder%2C%20has%20Pakistani%20origin%20and%20is%20likely%20facing%20similar%20visa%20issues%20like%20Australian%20batter%20Usman%20Khawaja%2C%20whose%20visa%2C%20too%2C%20arrived%20later%20for%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20India%20tour%20in%20early%202023.%20Khawaja%20was%20born%20in%20Islamabad.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20the%20fiasco%2C%20English%20captain%20Ben%20Stokes%20said%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Cfrustrated%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20delay%20with%20Bashir%E2%80%99s%20visa%20application%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Fben-stokes-frustrated-as-shoaib-bashir-returns-to-uk-to-resolve-visa-delay-1417904%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EESPNcricinfo%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20delay%20in%20Bashir%E2%80%99s%20visa%20processing%20has%20ruled%20him%20out%20of%20the%20first%20test%20between%20India%20and%20England%20between%20January%2025-29%2C%202024%20in%20Hyderabad.%20The%20squad%20had%20hoped%20that%20Bashir%20would%20eventually%20join%20the%20team%20but%20subsequent%20delays%20ruled%20out%20the%20possibility.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20initially%20hoped%20he%20would%20join%20his%20teammates%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Tuesday.%20But%20after%20further%20delays%2C%20the%2020-year-old%20has%20returned%20home%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20facilitating%20the%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilar%20delay%20was%20also%20experienced%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20during%20the%20ICC%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20last%20year%20when%20it%20could%20secure%20visas%20for%20its%20players%20only%20a%20day%20before%20they%20were%20scheduled%20to%20fly%20out.%20The%20delay%20forced%20the%20team%20to%20cancel%20its%20pre-season%20training%20camp%20in%20Dubai.%20Similarly%2C%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20Pakistani%20fans%20were%20also%20refused%20entry%20into%20India%20to%20watch%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20huge%20controversy%20with%20cricket%20commentators%20criticizing%20India%E2%80%99s%20adamant%20stance.%20The%20BCCI%20was%20also%20criticised%20for%20not%20facilitating%20the%20visa%20approvals%20on%20time.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20all%20other%20applications%20of%20his%20team%20members%2C%20Bashir%E2%80%99s%20application%20was%20submitted%20soon%20after%20December%2011%20when%20the%20squad%20was%20named.%20Another%20player%20with%20Pakistani%20origin%2C%20Rehan%20Ahmed%2C%20however%2C%20has%20joined%20the%20team%20after%20getting%20his%20visa%20as%20most%20of%20his%20paperwork%20was%20done%20before%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20when%20he%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20bench.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEspecially%20as%20captain%20I%20find%20it%20particularly%20frustrating.%20We%20announced%20that%20squad%20in%20mid-December%2C%20and%20now%20Bash%20finds%20himself%20without%20a%20visa%20to%20get%20here.%20I%20am%20more%20frustrated%20for%20him.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20this%20type%20of%20situation%20to%20be%20his%20first%20experience%20of%20what%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20to%20be%20in%20the%20England%20Test%20team.%20I%20feel%20for%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20Stokes%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20first%20cricketer%20to%20go%20through%20this%2C%20I%20have%20played%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20have%20had%20the%20same%20issues.%20I%20find%20it%20frustrating%20that%20we%20have%20picked%20a%20player%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20with%20us%20because%20of%20visa%20issues.%20Especially%20for%20a%20young%20lad%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20devastated%20for%20him.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20frustrating%20situation%20to%20be%20in%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20it%20through.%20It%E2%80%99s%20unfortunate%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20very%20frustrated%20for%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBashir%20played%20impressively%20in%20a%20camp%20in%20November%20and%20earned%20himself%20a%20place%20in%20the%20national%20squad.%20The%20six-foot-four%20offspinner%20is%20said%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Ca%20healthy%20amount%20of%20revolutions%20on%20the%20ball%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20selection%20despite%20an%20ordinary%20first%20class%20record.%20He%20performed%20outstandingly%20at%20the%20Abu%20Dhabi%20camp%20and%20was%20touted%20as%20an%20offset%20in%20Indian%20spin%20bowling%20conditions.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHim%20not%20being%20able%20to%20be%20here%20rules%20him%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Stokes%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20here%20with%20preconceived%20ideas%20about%20what%20we%20will%20do%20with%20the%20first%20team.%20In%20India%20you%20do%20like%20to%20have%20a%20good%20look%20at%20the%20pitch%20to%20see%20how%20it%20might%20play.%20With%20Bash%20unfortunately%20not%20able%20to%20be%20here%2C%20it%20rules%20him%20out%20of%20this%20game.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERenowned%20Australian%20cricket%20writer%20Peter%20Lalor%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20compare%20Bashir%E2%80%99s%20case%20with%20that%20of%20Khawaja.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFunny%20how%20Usman%20Khawaja%20and%20now%20Shoaib%20Bashir%20both%20have%20visa%20issues%20getting%20into%20India.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSjTZqU4EH8%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSjTZqU4EH8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Peter%20Lalor%20(%40plalor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fplalor%2Fstatus%2F1749610492153528574%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706118062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F24230333%2FEffect-82.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbritish-cricketer-shoaib-bashir-gets-indian-visa-finally-after-uk-govt-intervened-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Persons%20of%20Pakistani%20heritage%20appear%20to%20have%20different%20rules%20for%20them%2C%20commentators%20alluded%2C%20with%20Bashir%20following%20just%20months%20after%20Australian%20cricketer%20Usman%20Khwaja%20too%20had%20to%20face%20delays.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbritish-cricketer-shoaib-bashir-gets-indian-visa-finally-after-uk-govt-intervened-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon's%20record%20drought%20driven%20by%20climate%20change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706117855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F28A1%2Fproduction%2F_132410401_mediaitem132410400.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68032361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world's%20largest%20rainforest%20protects%20us%20from%20climate%20change%20but%20deforestation%20has%20left%20it%20vulnerable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68032361%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68032361.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68