ata-steel-returns-to-profit-in-q3-posts-pat-of-rs-513-cr-revenue-dips-3-124012401078_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ftata-steel-returns-to-profit-in-q3-posts-pat-of-rs-513-cr-revenue-dips-3-124012401078_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ftata-steel-returns-to-profit-in-q3-posts-pat-of-rs-513-cr-revenue-dips-3-124012401078_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Important%20Pillar%20of%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc'%3A%20Congress%20After%20TMC%20Reiterates%20Solo%20Act%20for%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F15162017%2FScreenshot-2023-02-15-at-4.19.30-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hours%20after%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20announced%20that%20she%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-bengal-congress-and-tmc-spar-rahul-gandhi-insists-seat-sharing-talks-still-on%5C%22%3Ego%20it%20alone%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Congress%20on%20Wednesday%20sought%20to%20contain%20the%20damage%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20said%20that%20she%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20pillar%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20bloc%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cspeed%20breakers%E2%80%9D%20along%20the%20journey%20do%20not%20imply%20an%20end%20to%20the%20journey%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20has%20reiterated%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20position%20and%20said%20that%20in%20West%20Bengal%20it%20is%20the%20only%20party%20that%20can%20defeat%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3ETMC%20spokesperson%20Sushmita%20Dev%20said%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20AITC%20(All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress)%20was%20very%20emphatically%20clear%20about%20finishing%20seat-sharing%20talks%20by%20September%2030.%20But%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%20Then%20December%203%20came%20when%20the%20assembly%20election%20results%20were%20announced%20and%20then%20it%20was%20decided%20let%E2%80%99s%20conclude%20seat-sharing%20talks%20by%20December%2031.%20But%20even%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20In%20these%20circumstances%20the%20AITC%20chairperson%20(Banerjee)%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20if%20anybody%20can%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bengal%20it%20is%20the%20TMC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20the%20very%20idea%20behind%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added%20referring%20to%20the%20goal%20of%20defeating%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDev%20said%20that%20Banerjee%20is%20clear%20about%20working%20with%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20on%20a%20national%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDidi%20is%20crystal%20clear%20that%20she%20stands%20with%20the%20alliance%20for%20the%20simple%20reason%20it%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20country%20to%20fight%20the%20party%20that%20has%20harmed%20federalism%2C%20democracy%20and%20harmed%20every%20institution%20and%20she%20will%20not%20step%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Barpeta%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20general%20secretary%20media%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20imagine%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20without%20Mamata%3Cem%3Eji%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20(Banerjee%E2%80%99s)%20full%20statement%20says%20that%20we%20will%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20We%20will%20not%20take%20any%20step%20back%20to%20not%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20We%20are%20entering%20Bengal%20with%20this%20idea.%20When%20you%20are%20on%20a%20long%20journey%2C%20there%20can%20be%20some%20speed%20breakers%2C%20some%20red%20lights.%20This%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20we%20will%20leave%20the%20journey.%20We%20will%20cross%20the%20speed%20breakers%2C%20red%20lights%20will%20become%20green%20lights%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20same%20question%20was%20asked%20to%20Rahul%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20yesterday.%20And%20he%20said%20that%20Mamata%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20big%20leader%2C%20of%20India%2C%20of%20Bengal%2C%20of%20the%20TMC%20and%20she%20is%20an%20important%20pillar%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20We%20cannot%20imagine%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20without%20Mamata%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20that%20what%20Mamata%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20that%20we%20will%20defeat%20BJP%20will%20remain%20the%20idea.%20The%20talks%20are%20on.%20Some%20middle%20path%20will%20emerge%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20fight%20the%20elections%20in%20West%20Bengal%20as%20an%20alliance%20and%20there%20will%20be%20cooperation%20among%20all%20the%20parties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20came%20hours%20after%20Banerjee%20told%20reporters%20that%20she%20will%20go%20it%20alone%20at%20least%20in%20Bengal%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20be%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20given%20them%20a%20proposal%20and%20they%20had%20turned%20it%20down.%20Since%20then%20we%20had%20decided%20that%20we%20will%20go%20it%20alone%20in%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20which%20will%20enter%20West%20Bengal%20through%20Cooch%20Behar%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Banerjee%20said%20that%20she%20had%20not%20been%20informed%20about%20the%20yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20doing%20a%20yatra%2C%20but%20have%20they%20even%20informed%20me%20even%20once%20that%20we%20are%20coming%20to%20your%20state%3F%20No%20they%20have%20not.%20Hence%20I%20have%20no%20communication%20with%20them%20about%20Bengal.%20We%20will%20think%20about%20what%20to%20do%20or%20not%20to%20do%20on%20an%20all-India%20level%2C%20we%20are%20a%20secular%20party%20and%20we%20will%20do%20everything%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20said%20during%20his%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20already%20invited%20all%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKharge%20(Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge)%20has%20already%20spoken%2C%20Rahulji%20has%20also%20spoken%20about%20it.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20written%20invitation%20I%20will%20check%20and%20let%20you%20know.%20But%20I%20know%20that%20Khargeji%20has%20already%20said%20at%20least%20three%20or%20four%20times%20in%20his%20speeches%20that%20we%20are%20inviting%20all%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20and%20he%20has%20spoken%20to%20every%20alliance%20partner.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20in%20what%20context%20she%20has%20said%20this.%20But%20I%20know%20she%20has%20said%20that%20we%20will%20defeat%20BJP%20and%20with%20this%20idea%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20will%20enter%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20when%20reports%20emerged%20that%20Banerjee%20had%20suffered%20injuries%20on%20her%20way%20back%20from%20Burdwan%20to%20Kolkata%20in%20an%20accident%2C%20Ramesh%20promptly%20tweeted%20that%20the%20Congress%20wished%20her%20a%20speedy%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20just%20heard%20of%20the%20injury%20suffered%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee-ji%20in%20a%20car%20accident.%20We%20wish%20her%20a%20full%20and%20speedy%20recovery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20just%20heard%20of%20the%20injury%20suffered%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee-ji%20in%20a%20car%20accident.%20We%20wish%20her%20a%20full%20and%20speedy%20recovery.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn