.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-1-1706104250.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339622%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Johnson%20Varghese's%20quest%20for%20highlighting%20the%20different%20uses%20of%20bamboos%20and%20its%20long-term%20benefits%20led%20him%20to%20build%20a%2017-acre%20farm%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20district%20that%20has%20been%20facing%20severe%20desertification.%20He%20has%20collected%20and%20conserved%20142%20rare%20species%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339622%2Frare-species-of-bamboo-in-kerala-india-farming-for-sustainable-future-desertification%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blow%20to%20Foreign%20Dreams%20of%20Punjabis%20As%20Canada%20Puts%20Two-Year%20Cap%20on%20Student%20Visas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14132814%2F41.-Travel-agencies_-India.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20major%20setback%20for%20lakhs%20of%20students%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20aspiring%20to%20study%20and%20settle%20in%20Canada%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20January%2023%2C%20announced%20a%20two-year%20cap%20on%20international%20student%20visas%2C%20besides%20other%20changes%2C%20leading%20to%20anxiety%20among%20students%20and%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20International%20English%20Language%20Testing%20Skills%20(IELTS)%20centres%2C%20where%20one%20can%20easily%20find%20more%20students%20than%20those%20in%20the%20colleges%2C%20to%20people%20across%20villages%20and%20in%20the%20cities%2C%20the%20only%20topic%20of%20discussion%20has%20been%20the%20Canadian%20government%20putting%20a%20cap%20on%20student%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20was%20made%20by%20Canadian%20minister%20of%20immigration%2C%20refugees%2C%20and%20citizenship%20(IRCC)%20Marc%20Miller%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20January%2023%2C%20in%20Ottawa.%20Miller%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CInternational%20students%20enrich%20our%20communities%20and%20are%20a%20critical%20part%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20social%2C%20cultural%20and%20economic%20fabric.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20international%20student%20system%20has%20been%20threatened.%20Some%20institutions%20have%20significantly%20increased%20their%20intakes%20to%20drive%20revenues%20and%20more%20students%20have%20been%20arriving%20in%20Canada%20without%20the%20proper%20support%20they%20need%20to%20succeed.%20Rapid%20increases%20in%20the%20number%20of%20international%20students%20arriving%20in%20Canada%20also%20put%20pressure%20on%20housing%2C%20health%20care%20and%20other%20services.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cap%20meant%20for%20two%20years%20would%20lead%20to%20a%2035%25%20overall%20reduction%20in%20new%20study%20visa%20permits%20this%20year%20and%20around%20a%2050%25%20decline%20in%20Ontario%20province%20alone%2C%20where%20bulk%20students%20were%20heading%20to%20popular%20colleges%20like%20Humber%2C%20Sheridan%2C%20Lambton%2C%20Centennial%2C%20and%20George%20Brown%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20study%20visa%20rules%20was%20almost%20imminent%2C%20as%20last%20year%20the%20Canadian%20government%20had%20increased%20the%20Guaranteed%20Certificate%20Limit%20(GIC)%20amount%2C%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20for%20a%20study%20visa%20permit%20from%20CAD%2010%2C000%20to%20CAD%2020%2C635%2C%20which%20means%20Rs%2012.58%20lakh%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20amount%20of%20Rs%206%20lakh.%20This%20directly%20increased%20the%20overall%20study%20visa%20expenses%20to%20almost%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20reason%20behind%20this%20decision%20has%20also%20been%20the%20housing%20crisis%20and%20inflation%20in%20Canada%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20immigrants%20to%20sustain%2C%20a%20topic%20that%20has%20remained%20in%20the%20news.%20However%2C%20despite%20this%20fact%2C%20Canada%20is%20still%20the%20most%20sought-after%20country%20among%20students%20in%20Punjab%20for%20the%20sheer%20reason%20that%20it%20offers%20a%20Permanent%20Residency%20(PR)%20option%20within%20a%20period%20of%20three%20years.%20Other%20than%20Canada%2C%20students%20have%20also%20been%20moving%20to%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%E2%80%99s%20change%20in%20study%20visa%20rules%20has%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20sour%20diplomatic%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%2C%20which%20hit%20the%20international%20headlines%20last%20year.%20In%20September%20last%20year%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20accused%20the%20Indian%20agencies%20of%20killing%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20series%20of%20diplomatic%20moves%20affecting%20both%20the%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14133234%2F40.-Travel-agencies_-India.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14133234%2F40.-Travel-agencies_-India.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14133234%2F40.-Travel-agencies_-India-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14133234%2F40.-Travel-agencies_-India-1024x684.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-648528%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22801%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJalandhar%E2%80%99s%20travel%20agencies.%20Photo%3A%20Stefania%20Prandi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPunjabis%20selling%20assets%20to%20send%20children%20to%20Canada%3A%20study%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20in-depth%20study%20on%20%3Cem%3EOverseas%20Migration%20from%20Rural%20Punjab%3A%20Trends%2C%20Causes%2C%20and%20Consequences%3C%2Fem%3E%20conducted%20by%20three%20professors%20of%20the%20sociology%20department%20from%20Punjab%20Agricultural%20University%20(PAU)%2C%20Ludhiana%20found%20that%20about%2056%25%20of%20households%20borrowed%20money%20to%20send%20their%20children%20abroad.%20Canada%20was%20the%20first%20choice%20among%20applicants%20followed%20by%20Dubai%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20conducted%20by%20professors%20Shalini%20Sharma%2C%20Manjeet%20Kaur%2C%20and%20assistant%20professor%20Amit%20Guleria%20from%20the%20year%202021%20to%202023%20found%20that%20Punjabis%20sold%20assets%20worth%20Rs%205%2C636%20crore%20and%20borrowed%20a%20total%20amount%20of%20Rs%2014%2C%20342%20crore%20to%20send%20their%20children%20abroad.%20On%20average%2C%20a%20family%20in%20Punjab%20spends%20around%20Rs%2018%20to%2025%20lakh%20on%20a%20study%20visa%20and%20up%20to%20Rs%204%20lakh%20on%20other%20visas%2C%20including%20those%20moving%20to%20Dubai%20on%20work%20visas%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20Around%2071.88%25%20of%20people%20moving%20abroad%20were%20engaged%20in%20agriculture%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20interesting%20fact%20was%20that%20of%20the%20total%20migrants%2C%2073.16%25%20moved%20abroad%20after%202016.%20Among%20male%20migrants%2C%2043.15%25%20went%20on%20a%20work%20visa%20and%2033.73%25%20on%20a%20study%20visa.%20The%20education%20level%20of%20female%20migrants%20was%20also%20way%20too%20high%20than%20that%20of%20males%20at%2037.25%25%20of%20graduates%20and%20above.%20The%20males%E2%80%99%20education%20level%20was%2017.47%25%20and%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanged%20immigration%20policies%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%2C%20Canadian%20minister%20Marc%20Miller%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20of%20Canada%20will%20set%20an%20intake%20cap%20on%20international%20student%20permit%20applications%20to%20stabilise%20new%20growth%20for%20a%20period%20of%20two%20years.%20For%202024%2C%20the%20cap%20is%20expected%20to%20result%20in%20approximately%203%2C60%2C000%20approved%20study%20permits%2C%20a%20decrease%20of%2035%20percent%20from%202023.%20Study%20permit%20renewals%20will%20not%20be%20impacted.%20Those%20pursuing%20master%E2%80%99s%20and%20doctoral%20degrees%20and%20elementary%20and%20secondary%20education%20are%20not%20included%20in%20the%20cap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiller%20also%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThese%20temporary%20measures%20will%20be%20in%20place%20for%20two%20years%20and%20the%20number%20of%20new%20study%20permit%20applications%20that%20will%20be%20accepted%20in%202025%20will%20be%20re-assessed%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20change%20was%20also%20announced%20for%20Spouse%20Visa%20cases%2C%20under%20which%20in%20the%20weeks%20ahead%2C%20open%20work%20permits%20will%20only%20be%20available%20to%20spouses%20of%20international%20students%20in%20master%E2%80%99s%20and%20doctoral%20programs%20along%20with%20medicine%20and%20law.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20spouses%20of%20international%20students%20in%20other%20levels%20of%20study%2C%20including%20undergraduate%20and%20college%20programs%2C%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20eligible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDampener%20for%20students%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20government%E2%80%99s%20cap%20of%20two%20years%20on%20study%20visas%20came%20as%20a%20dampener%20for%20all%20the%20students%2C%20with%20many%20stating%20that%20they%20might%20consider%20moving%20to%20the%20US%2C%20UK%20or%20Australia.%20However%2C%20most%20of%20the%20students%20said%20that%20they%20still%20prefer%20Canada%20as%20the%20best%20country%20to%20move%20and%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20reason%20behind%20students%20from%20Punjab%20moving%20in%20bulk%20to%20Canada%20was%20that%20they%20were%20migrating%20with%20their%20friends%20and%20cousins.%20Interestingly%2C%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20students%20used%20to%20plan%20admissions%20in%20the%20best%20colleges%20and%20universities%20in%20Punjab.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20this%20trend%20shifted%20to%20students%20searching%20for%20famous%20colleges%20in%20Canada%2C%20hence%20draining%20nearly%20all%20the%20colleges%20of%20funds%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0spoke%20to%20students%20at%20different%20IELTS%20centres%20in%20and%20around%20Jalandhar%2C%20who%20appeared%20disheartened%20and%20apprehensive%20about%20their%20prospects%20in%20Canada.%20Even%20at%20the%20IELTS%20centres%2C%20where%20earlier%20students%20would%20rush%20to%20inquire%20about%20IELTS%20coaching%20and%20fees%2C%20the%20queries%20were%20confined%20to%20how%20they%20can%20get%20study%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Touchstone%20IELTS%20Academy%2C%20Jalandhar%2C%20three%20applicants%20who%20came%20for%20a%20counselling%20session%20said%20that%20they%20were%20aware%20of%20the%20new%20study%20visa%20rules%20and%20wanted%20to%20clear%20their%20doubts.%20One%20among%20them%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20new%20changes%20announced%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government.%20I%20would%20rather%20go%20to%20the%20US%20to%20study%2C%20than%20consider%20Canada.%E2%80%9D%20The%20other%20two%20students%20said%20that%20they%20would%20try%20for%20a%20Canada%20study%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapurthala%20district-based%20boys%20Anmol%20and%20Gurcharan%2C%20class%20XII%20students%2C%20and%20IELTS%20students%20at%20Touchstone%20Academy%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20these%20circumstances%2C%20we%20might%20consider%20moving%20to%20the%20UK%20or%20Australia.%20Given%20the%20number%20of%20international%20students%20in%20Canada%2C%20these%20changes%20were%20bound%20to%20take%20place%20sooner%20than%20later.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Canam%20Consultants%2C%20Jalandhar%2C%20Inderjit%20Kaur%2C%20an%20IELTS%20student%20was%20disheartened%20to%20learn%20that%20the%20open%20work%20permit%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20available%20to%20spouses%20of%20graduate%20programs.%20A%20class%20XII%20pass%20out%2C%20Inderjit%E2%80%99s%20fianc%C3%A9%20was%20in%20Dubai%20and%20the%20couple%20was%20planning%20to%20get%20married%20soon.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20planning%20to%20move%20to%20Canada%20on%20a%20study%20visa%20and%20invite%20my%20husband%20on%20a%20Spouse%20visa.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20rethink%20and%20plan%20accordingly%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20student%20visa%20applicant%2C%20Neha%20from%20Lambra%2C%20Jalandhar%20said%20that%20she%20had%20already%20made%20up%20her%20mind%20to%20move%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20instead%20of%20Canada%20because%20of%20several%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20she%20was%20desperate%20to%20move%20abroad%2C%20the%20student%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20point%20paying%20hefty%20fees%20here%20in%20India%20and%20working%20on%20meager%20salaries%20of%20just%20Rs%2010%2C%20000%20to%20Rs%2012%2C000%20and%20ruining%20your%20life.%20It%20is%20better%20to%20spend%20that%20money%20on%20moving%20abroad%20through%20study%20permits%2C%20find%20work%20and%20earn%20well.%20There%20is%20no%20future%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisa%20consultants%20affected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20visa%20consultant%20of%20a%20leading%20IELTS%20Academy%20in%20Jalandhar%20with%20branches%20across%20the%20region%20said%20that%20they%20were%20already%20expecting%20these%20changes%2C%20which%20clearly%20means%20that%20the%20Canadian%20government%20will%20now%20focus%20only%20on%20the%20creamy%20students.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20yet%20to%20get%20clarity%20on%20how%20the%2035%25%20reduction%20in%20study%20visas%20will%20be%20implemented%20but%20surely%2C%20this%20will%20lead%20to%20more%20scrutiny%20of%20applications%20and%20study%20visa%20refusal.%20Our%20understanding%20is%20that%20the%20Canadian%20government%20might%20demand%20higher%20IELTS%20and%20academic%20scores%20and%20strict%20admission%20policy%20in%20various%20courses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consultant%20also%20said%20that%20now%20students%20with%2010%20to%2012%20years%20of%20education%20gap%20would%20not%20be%20entertained%20as%20was%20the%20case%20earlier.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20become%20difficult%20to%20get%20a%20Canada%20study%20visa%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20Canada%20is%20not%20just%20the%20sought%20after%20destination%20to%20move%20abroad%20among%20students%20but%20for%20applicants%20in%20other%20categories%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20there%20was%20more%20hype%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20jobs%20in%20Canada%20than%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20entire%20Canada%20was%20not%20affected%20with%20joblessness.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20problem%20was%20more%20evident%20in%20Provinces%20like%20Ontario%2C%20where%20the%20concentration%20of%20international%20students%20was%20way%20too%20high%20as%20compared%20to%20other%20places.%20We%20have%20been%20suggesting%20students%20to%20opt%20for%20Nova%20Scotia%2C%20Alberta%20and%20Winnipeg%2C%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20face%20this%20crisis%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20consultant%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%20Rao%2C%20Managing%20Director%20of%20Golden%20Pillars%20IELTS%20Academy%2C%20Jalandhar%20said%20that%20it%20is%20simple%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20will%20be%20issuing%20less%20study%20visas%20now.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20reduction%20means%20that%20students%20with%20higher%20IELTS%20scores%20would%20be%20considered%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20those%20just%20fulfilling%20the%20basic%20criteria%20of%206%20band%20each%20in%20all%20IELTS%20modules%20and%20an%20overall%206%20score.%20Even%20the%20course%20selection%20will%20matter%20a%20lot%20now%2C%20which%20means%20that%20students%20opting%20for%20professional%20courses%20will%20get%20study%20visa%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consultant%20also%20said%20that%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20were%20the%20first%20ones%20to%20start%20a%20study%20visa%20system%20around%20two%20decades%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20number%20of%20applicants%20these%20countries%20wanted%20were%20taken%20in%2C%20they%20made%20the%20selection%20criteria%20for%20study%20visa%20strict.%20Canada%20is%20also%20doing%20the%20same%20and%20has%20introduced%20a%20cap%20of%20two-years.%20The%20Canadian%20authorities%20might%20rethink%20about%20migration%20two%20years%20from%20now%20but%20as%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Canadian%20dream%20has%20come%20to%20a%20halt%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20Punjabis%2C%20people%20have%20been%20moving%20to%20Canada%20from%20across%20the%20world%20through%20different%20immigration%20programs.%20%E2%80%9CCanada%20might%20plan%20about%20developing%20some%20other%20provinces%20and%20cities%2C%20where%20there%20was%20no%20infrastructure%20and%20houses.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20even%20for%20that%2C%20they%20need%20time.%20So%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20will%20be%20implementing%20checks%20on%20the%20study%20visa%20process%20and%20surely%20many%20candidates%20will%20be%20affected%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706105778000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14132814%2F41.-Travel-agencies_-India.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fblow-to-foreign-dreams-of-punjabis-as-canada-puts-two-year-cap-on-student-visas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20changed%20immigration%20policies%20of%20Canada%20not%20only%20affect%20lakhs%20of%20students%20but%20also%20an%20entire%20gamut%20of%20professionals%20offering%20consulting%20services%20i