nge%2C%20the%20change%20in%20the%20previous%20period%2C%20i.e.%202005-06%20to%202015-16%2C%20was%20slower%20(-7.69%25)%20than%20that%20during%202015-16%20to%202019-21%20(-10.66%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20paper%20extrapolates%20the%20multidimensional%20poverty%20index%20(MPI)%20for%202014-15%20and%202022-23%20and%20argues%20that%20almost%2025%20crore%20people%20have%20escaped%20poverty%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20these%20projections%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fniti-aayong-national-poverty-indicator%5C%22%3Eno%20basis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20considering%20that%20during%20this%20period%2C%20the%20country%20has%20faced%20major%20health%20and%20economic%20shocks%20because%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20there%20has%20been%20an%20improvement%20in%20many%20of%20the%20indicators%20included%20in%20the%20MPI%20over%20the%20last%2020%20years.%20But%20the%20question%20remains%3A%20is%20this%20sufficient%20to%20claim%20not%20only%20that%20poverty%20has%20declined%20but%20that%20it%20has%20done%20so%20at%20a%20faster%20pace%20during%20the%20two%20terms%20of%20the%20present%20government%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20MPI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20Amartya%20Sen%E2%80%99s%20theory%20of%20capabilities%20and%20functioning%2C%20the%20HDI%20(Human%20Development%20Index)%20and%20MPI%20expand%20focus%20away%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98means%E2%80%99%20(income)%20to%20%E2%80%98ends%E2%80%99%20(expanding%20choices%2Fcapabilities).%20This%20has%20been%20an%20important%20development%20as%20it%20enables%20policy%20discussion%20to%20also%20move%20from%20a%20single-minded%20focus%20on%20increasing%20GDP%20to%20looking%20at%20the%20outcomes%20for%20people%20and%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGDP%20growth%20or%20higher%20per%20capita%20incomes%20do%20not%20necessarily%20always%20translate%20into%20better%20education%2C%20nutrition%20or%20health%20outcomes.%20This%20is%20best%20seen%20in%20the%20case%20of%20India%20compared%20to%20neighbouring%20Bangladesh%20or%20Nepal%2C%20which%20have%20lower%20per%20capita%20incomes%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnarendra-modi-govt-world-bank-human-capital-index%5C%22%3Ebetter%3C%2Fa%3E%20human%20development%20indicators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20within%20India%2C%20the%20ranking%20of%20states%20by%20per%20capita%20income%20does%20not%20exactly%20match%20the%20ranking%20by%20human%20development%20indicators.%20Southern%20states%2C%20particularly%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-62951951%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20known%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20achieved%20relatively%20better%20health%20and%20education%20outcomes%20through%20progressive%20social%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fhunger-undernutrition-stalking-india-placed-worse-than-least-developed-nations-prabhat-patnaik%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Hunger%2C%20Undernutrition%20Stalking%20India%3B%20Placed%20Worse%20Than%20Least%20Developed%20Nations%E2%80%99%3A%20Prabhat%20Patnaik%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MPI%20measures%20deprivations%20across%20health%2C%20education%20and%20living%20standards%20with%20equal%20weightage%20being%20given%20to%20these%20three%20dimensions.%20Health%20includes%20nutrition%20and%20child%20and%20adolescent%20mortality%3B%20education%20includes%20years%20of%20schooling%20and%20school%20attendance%3B%20and%20standard%20of%20living%20includes%20cooking%20fuel%2C%20sanitation%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20housing%2C%20assets%2C%20and%20bank%20accounts.%20The%20indicators%20within%20each%20dimension%20are%20given%20the%20same%20weight.%20Therefore%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20education%20dimension%20has%20two%20indicators%20of%20deprivation%2C%20each%20of%20which%20has%20a%20weight%20of%201%2F3*1%2F2%20%3D%201%2F6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20household%20is%20given%20a%20deprivation%20score%20based%20on%20whether%20the%20household%20is%20deprived%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20these%20chosen%20indicators%20(1%20if%20deprived%20and%200%20if%20not)%2C%20and%20then%20the%20weighted%20total%20in%20percentage%20terms%20is%20the%20deprivation%20score.%20If%20the%20deprivation%20score%20of%20a%20household%20is%20more%20than%2033%25%2C%20then%20this%20household%20is%20identified%20as%20being%20multidimensionally%20poor.%20The%20proportion%20of%20multidimensionally%20poor%20(weighted%20by%20household%20size)%20gives%20the%20head%20count%20ratio%20or%20the%20proportion%20of%20poor%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20since%20each%20household%20is%20given%20a%20score%20based%20on%20their%20deprivations%20across%20dimensions%2C%20this%20methodology%20also%20allows%20us%20to%20understand%20the%20intensity%20of%20poverty%20at%20the%20household%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20National%20MPI%20(NMPI)%20uses%20the%20same%20methodology%2C%20but%20has%20added%20two%20further%20indicators%20%E2%80%93%20maternal%20health%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98health%E2%80%99%20dimension%20and%20financial%20inclusion%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98standard%20of%20living%E2%80%99%20dimension.%20As%20with%20any%20multidimensional%20index%2C%20there%20can%20be%20a%20valid%20debate%20on%20which%20indicators%20are%20included%20and%20what%20the%20method%20for%20aggregating%20them%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20NMPI%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20method%20of%20aggregation%20results%20in%20child%20and%20adolescent%20mortality%20being%20given%20a%20weightage%20of%201%2F12%2C%20whereas%20school%20attendance%20has%20the%20weightage%20of%201%2F6%20and%20having%20a%20bank%20account%20is%20weighted%201%2F21.%20Without%20going%20into%20the%20merits%20or%20demerits%20of%20the%20weighting%20matrix%2C%20the%20issue%20is%20that%20the%20limits%20of%20what%20the%20MPI%20indicates%20must%20be%20understood%20clearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20choice%20of%20indicators%2C%20as%20has%20been%20shown%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fpoverty-measure-niti-aayog-decline%5C%22%3Eothers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20MPI%20includes%20both%20input%20and%20outcome%20indicators.%20Therefore%2C%20while%20we%20have%20a%20household%20being%20deprived%20if%20there%20was%20a%20child%20or%20an%20adolescent%20death%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20(outcome)%2C%20another%20indicator%20is%20on%20whether%20the%20family%20has%20electricity%20supply%20(input).%20If%20one%20looks%20at%20other%20inputs%2C%20such%20as%20the%20supplementary%20nutrition%20or%20school%20meals%20provided%20to%20children%2C%20then%20there%20is%20a%20deterioration%20given%20the%20decline%20in%20Union%20budgets%20for%20these%20programmes%20over%20the%20last%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20even%20along%20a%20single%20dimension%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20understood%20that%20the%20MPI%20does%20not%20give%20a%20full%20picture.%20For%20example%2C%20by%20the%20nutrition%20indicator%2C%20a%20household%20is%20deprived%20if%20a%20child%20under%20five%20or%20an%20adult%20man%20or%20a%20woman%20is%20undernourished%20as%20defined%20by%20anthropometric%20indicators.%20Therefore%2C%20even%20though%20the%20prevalence%20of%20anaemia%20has%20increased%20between%20NFHS-4%20and%205%20(2015-16%20to%202019-21)%2C%20the%20nutrition%20indicator%20shows%20an%20improvement.%20The%20MPI%20also%20does%20not%20tell%20us%20anything%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20improvements.%20So%2C%20we%20can%20have%20the%20education%20indicator%20improving%20rapidly%2C%20while%20the%20learning%20outcomes%20as%20shown%20by%20repeated%20ASER%20data%20remain%20appalling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20other%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20methodology%20that%20have%20been%20actively%20discussed%20in%20the%20literature%20around%20measurement%20of%20poverty%20and%20development.%20Without%20going%20into%20those%20details%2C%20it%20is%20broadly%20understood%20that%20the%20MPI%20adds%20value%20to%20our%20understanding%20of%20poverty%20and%20development%20by%20taking%20attention%20away%20solely%20from%20money-based%20indicators%20such%20as%20per%20capita%20incomes%20or%20consumption%20expenditure%20to%20actual%20achievements%2C%20such%20as%20being%20educated%20or%20being%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20MPI%20has%20been%20included%20as%20one%20of%20the%20indicators%20of%20development%20in%20the%20UNDP%E2%80%99s%20Human%20Development%20Reports%20(HDR)%20and%20the%20NMPI%20is%20the%20indicator%20for%20one%20of%20the%20targets%20of%20the%20SDG%20Goal%20One%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fsustainabledevelopment%2Fpoverty%2F%5C%22%3Eending%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Based%20on%20this%2C%20it%20is%20being%20claimed%20that%20India%20is%20on%20the%20path%20to%20meeting%20this%20goal.%20SDG%20Goal%20One%20also%20includes%20targets%20on%20the%20proportion%20of%20population%20living%20below%20the%20national%20and%20international%20poverty%20lines%2C%20for%20which%20we%20have%20no%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20MPI%20takes%20us%20forward%20as%20it%20draws%20attention%20to%20a%20multidimensional%20understanding%20of%20poverty%20%E2%80%93%20poverty%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20incomes%20or%20consumption%20expenditure%20but%20across%20different%20dimensions%2C%20tracking%20individual%20indicators%20is%20critical%20for%20policy%20purposes%20and%20the%20limits%20of%20any%20multidimensional%20indicator%20should%20be%20understood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Feconomists-say-niti-aayog-claims-on-poverty-reduction-distort-the-truth%5C%22%3EEconomists%20Say%20NITI%20Aayog%20Claims%20on%20Poverty%20Reduction%20Distort%20the%20Truth%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMPI%20and%20consumption%20expenditure%3A%20complementary%20and%20necessary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20by%20giving%20up%20on%20income%20and%20consumption%20indicators%20entirely%20and%20only%20focussing%20on%20MPI%20to%20measure%20poverty%20is%20also%20not%20appropriate.%20Household%20incomes%20are%20difficult%20to%20measure%20accurately%20in%20a%20developing%20country%20like%20India%2C%20where%20there%20is%20a%20large%20informal%20sector%20with%20irregular%20and%20multiple%20sources%20of%20income.%20Consumption%20expenditure%20has%20been%20used%20as%20a%20proxy%20for%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumption%20expenditure%20gives%20an%20estimate%20of%20how%20the%20purchasing%20power%20of%20households%20is%20changing%20and%20can%20indicate%20the%20immediate%20short-term%20impact%20of%20macroeconomic%20trends.%20An%20increase%20in%20or%20slow%20decrease%20in%20poverty%20based%20on%20consumption%20expenditure%2C%20along%20with%20increasing%20national%20income%2C%20indicates%20that%20the%20growth%20is%20unevenly%20distributed%20and%20is%20not%20reaching%20the%20poorer%20sections.%20At%20the%20household%20level%2C%20income%20is%20still%20an%20important%20determinant%20(although%20not%20the%20only%20one)%20of%20access%20to%20most%20goods%20and%20services%2C%20and%20hence%20human%20development%20outcomes%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20poverty%20was%20usually%20measured%20based%20on%20households%20that%20had%20a%20monthly%20per%20capita%20consumption%20expenditure%20(MPCE)%20below%20an%20officially%20designated%20poverty%20line.%20The%20level%20at%20which%20the%20poverty%20line%20is%20set%20has%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20great%20public%20debate%2C%20with%20various%20committees%20having%20been%20set%20up%20to%20update%20the%20poverty%20line.%20The%20most%20recent%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fopinion-what-happened-to-poverty-estimation-in-the-country-1552584031417.html%5C%22%3ERangarajan%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20submitted%20its%20report%20in%202014.%20It%20is%2C%20however%2C%20not%20clear%20whether%20India%20now%20even%20has%20an%20official%20poverty%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20available%20official%20consumption%20expenditure%20data%20on%20which%20poverty%20estimates%20are%20based%20is%20for%202011-12.%20Although%20NSS%20conducted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Feconomy-policy%2Fgovt-scraps-nso-s-consumer-expenditure-survey-over-data-quality-119111501838_1.html%5C%22%3Econsumption%20expenditure%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202017-18%2C%20this%20report%20was%20junked%20by%20the%20government%20without%20adequate%20explanation.%20A%20leaked%20version%20of%20the%20report%20showed%20that%20the%20consumption%20expenditure%20of%20the%20poor%20had%20fallen%2C%20probably%20indicating%20an%20increase%20in%20poverty%20in%20the%20period%20immediately%20following%20demonetisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumption%20expenditure%20data%20can%20also%20throw%20light%20on%20the%20current%20discussion%20on%20whether%20the%20revival%20in%20growth%20is%20V-shaped%20or%20K-shaped%20as%20well%20as%20inequality%20by%20class%20and%20social%20group%2C%20change%20in%20patterns%20of%20food%20and%20non-food%20consumption%2C%20the%20effect%20of%20expanded%20public%20distribution%20system%2C%20or%20PDS%2C%20on%20food%20consumption%20and%20many%20more%20important%20issues.%20Further%2C%20including%20consumption%20expenditure-based%20poverty%20ratios%20in%20our%20analysis%20allows%20for%20a%20longer-term%20analysis%20of%20poverty%20in%20the%20country%2C%20whereas%20the%20MPI%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%20NFHS%20data%2C%20is%20only%20possible%20for%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-74-indians-unable-to-afford-healthy-diet-un-report%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Over%2074%25%20Indians%20Unable%20to%20Afford%20Healthy%20Diet%E2%80%99%3A%20UN%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20data%2C%20better%20analysis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20MPI%20alone%2C%20claiming%20that%20all%20the%20recent%20initiatives%20of%20the%20government%2C%20ranging%20from%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fanemiamuktbharat.info%2F%5C%22%3E%20Anaemia%20Mukt%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E%20(anaemia%20is%20not%20even%20included%20in%20the%20MPI!)%20to%20free%20grains%20in%20the%20PDS%20(introduced%20only%20in%202020%20after%20half%20the%20NFHS%20survey%20was%20completed)%2C%20as%20is%20being%20done%20in%20various%20reports%20and%20press%20releases%20is%20a%20bit%20far-fetched.%20These%20programmes%20have%20to%20be%20analysed%20in%20their%20entirety%2C%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20fact%20that%20budgets%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbudget%2Fbudget-for-women-and-child-development-shrinks-poshan-slashed-by-27%2Farticle33721315.ece%5C%22%3EPoshan%20Abhiyan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20schemes%20have%20actually%20been%20slashed%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fgovernance%2Fas-2023-comes-to-a-close-govt-must-increase-coverage-of-free-foodgrain-886709%5C%22%3EPDS%20coverage%20has%20remained%20stagnant%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20Census%202011%20population%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20improvements%20in%20toilet%20access%20and%20bank%20accounts%20are%20easier%20to%20link%20to%20direct%20government%20schemes.%20Reviving%20India%E2%80%99s%20data%20ecosystem%20by%20conducting%20the%20Census%2C%20consumption%20expenditure%20survey%20and%20others%20would%20be%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20an%20honest%20analysis%20of%20what%20worked%20and%20what%20didn%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDipa%20Sinha%20is%20faculty%20at%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20University%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706094301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F28095433%2F1024px-Hatibagan_market_during_lockdown_02.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-multidimensional-poverty-index-is-not-all-encompassing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Improvements%20in%20toilet%20access%20and%20bank%20accounts%20are%20easier%20to%20link%20to%20direct%20government%20schemes%2C%20but%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20an%20honest%20analysis%20of%20what%20worked%20and%20what%20didn%E2%80%99t%20would%20be%20reviving%20India%E2%80%99s%20data%20ecosystem%20through%20conducting%20the%20Census%20and%20consumption%20expenditure%20survey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-multidimensional-poverty-index-is-not-all-encompassing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harry%20and%20Meghan%20attend%20Bob%20Marley%20film%20premiere%20in%20Jamaica%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706093940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-prince-harry-meghan_6431618.jpg%3F20240124110702%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fharry-and-meghan-attend-bob-marley-film-premiere-in-jamaica-13055275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harry%20and%20Meghan%20have%20been%20spotted%20on%20the%20red%20carpet%20in%20Jamaica%2C%20attending%20the%20premiere%20of%20a%20film%20celebrating%20the%20life%20of%20Bob%20Marley.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A240%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fharry-and-meghan-attend-bob-marley-film-premiere-in-jamaica-13055275%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fharry-and-meghan-attend-bob-marley-film-premiere-in-jamaica-13055275%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fharry-and-meghan-attend-bob-marley-film-premiere-in-jamaica-13055