le%2C%20the%20cook%20Sayed%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20was%20sleeping%20in%20the%20common%20passage%2C%20woke%20up%20and%20saw%20smoke%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20windows%20of%20the%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mumbai-based%20journalist%2C%20author%20and%20local%20historian%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdhavalkulkarni%2Fstatus%2F1745164531842888077%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDhaval%20Kulkarni%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20in%20his%20recent%20thread%20on%20X%20(Twitter)%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20main%20door%20of%20the%20flat%20was%20slightly%20ajar%20and%20he%20went%20in%20with%20Usman.%20They%20saw%20fire%20in%20the%20passage%20leading%20to%20the%20kitchen.%20This%20fire%20in%20newspapers%20and%20clothes%20was%20doused%20using%20buckets%20of%20water.%20Once%20the%20fire%20subsided%2C%20they%20were%20terrified%20to%20see%20human%20legs%20under%20the%20newspapers%20in%20a%20scorched%20condition.%20The%20watchman%20ran%20to%20the%20nearby%20Gamdevi%20police%20station%20and%20informed%20PSI%20(Police%20Sub-Inspector)%20Shivaji%20Deshmukh%2C%20who%20was%20on%20duty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Choonawala-Collage-1705586378.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Quadruple%20murder%20case%20in%20Bombay%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Choonawala-Collage-1705586378.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Choonawala-Collage-1705586378-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Choonawala-Collage-1705586378-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Choonawala-Collage-1705586378-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Choonawala-Collage-1705586378-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338578%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChoonawala%20family%20photo%20(L)%20and%20Temple%20View%20building%20entrance%20(R)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20was%20a%20gory%20quadruple%20murder%20case%2C%20the%20first%20in%20the%20then%20Bombay%2C%20and%20a%20remarkable%20investigation%20led%20by%20Bombay%20Police%20%5Bnow%20Mumbai%20Police%5D%20CID%20deputy%20commissioner%20Vaidyanath%20Someshwar%20Sami%2C%20the%20father%20of%20legendary%20singer%20Usha%20Uthup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopularly%20known%20as%20the%20Bombay%20Police%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F254655%2Fgeorge-edalji-sir-arthur-conan-doyle-real-life-sherlock-holmes-battle-mutilation-great-wyrley-england-captain-anson-racism-shrabani-basu-history-div200%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESherlock%20Holmes%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20Vaidyanath%20Sami%20and%20his%20officers%20caught%20the%20culprits%20of%20his%20horrific%20crime%20using%20the%20laundry%20mark%20(tag)%20of%20burnt%20pieces%20of%20clothing%20found%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20this%20horrific%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20they%20solved%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20the%20laundry%20mark%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Dhaval%20describes%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20%E2%80%9CDeshmukh%20and%20his%20team%20rushed%20to%20the%20scene%20and%20observed%20that%20the%20gas%20pipe%20in%20the%20kitchen%20was%20loose.%20He%20hence%20went%20to%20the%20kitchen%20and%20closed%20the%20gas%20connection.%20He%20found%20four%20bodies%20in%20the%20flat%20with%20multiple%20stab%20wounds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bodies%20had%20been%20covered%20with%20newspapers%20and%20clothes%2C%20and%20it%20appeared%20that%20an%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20set%20fire%20to%20the%20bodies%20and%20the%20flat%20as%20well%20by%20opening%20the%20gas%20pipe.%20The%20bedroom%20was%20ransacked%2C%20and%20cash%20and%20jewels%20were%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20goes%20on%20to%20add.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20were%20Choonawala%2C%20his%20wife%20Roshan%2C%20four-year-old%20grandson%20Shajitkhan%20%5B%20also%20spelled%20Sajid%20Khan%5D%2C%20and%20their%20house%20help%20Annie%20Fernandes.%20All%20four%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20stabbed%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Queen%20of%20Indian%20Pop%3A%20The%20Authorised%20Biography%20of%20Usha%20Uthup%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20written%20by%20Vikram%20Kumar%20Jha%20and%20translated%20by%20Srishti%20Jha%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BMohammad%20Siddiqui%5D%20Chunawala%20was%20a%20big%20businessman%20and%20his%20murder%20had%20put%20the%20Gamdevi%20Police%20Station%20in%20a%20deep%20shock.%20Curfew%20was%20enforced%20in%20the%20area%20under%20the%20police%20station%E2%80%99s%20jurisdiction.%20Ultimately%2C%20seeing%20no%20developments%20in%20this%20puzzling%20murder%20case%2C%20the%20inspector%20of%20the%20Gamdevi%20Police%20Station%20called%20%5BDCP%5D%20Vaidyanath%20Sami%20and%20communicated%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation.%20He%20requested%20the%20latter%20to%20help%20in%20the%20investigation.%E2%80%9D%20%5B*both%20the%20%E2%80%98Choonawala%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Chunawala%E2%80%98%20spellings%20have%20been%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20businessman%20murdered%20in%20this%20case*%5D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20request%2C%20DCP%20Vaidyanath%20dispatched%20his%20officers%20to%20the%20scene.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20evidence%3A%3Cbr%3ESoon%2C%20officers%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20CID-Crime%20or%20the%20Crime%20branch%20like%20inspector%20Vinayak%20Vakatkar%2C%20and%20sub-inspectors%20Tatyasaheb%20Goud%20and%20Ramchandra%20Dudhat%20arrived%20at%20the%20scene.%20They%20came%20to%20know%20that%20on%20the%20previous%20day%2C%20Choonawala%20had%20returned%20home%20from%20Radio%20Club%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzQjVJqsQzd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzQjVJqsQzd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dhaval%20Kulkarni%20(%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A3%E0%A5%80)%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40dhavalkulkarni)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdhavalkulkarni%2Fstatus%2F1745164537689747772%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinayak%20Vakatkar%20was%20a%20legendary%20officer%20in%20the%20Bombay%20Police%20crime%20branch.%20His%20cases%20and%20investigations%20made%20it%20to%20the%20newspapers%20and%20the%20works%20of%20local%20crime%20writers.%20Vakatkar%20eventually%20retired%20as%20an%20assistant%20commissioner%20of%20police.%20PSI%20Tatyasaheb%20Gaud%20retired%20as%20an%20ACP.%20An%20ace%20investigator%20with%20the%20Bombay%20Police%2C%20he%20was%20also%20a%20prolific%20writer%20in%20Marathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Police-Officers-1705586515.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Police%20solve%20murder%20case%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Police-Officers-1705586515.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Police-Officers-1705586515-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu