0clothes%20found%20at%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20Inspector%20Vakatkar%20located%2012%20laundries%20in%20the%20city%20which%20used%20this%20laundry%20mark.%20On%2024%20October%2C%20the%20police%20finally%20zeroed%20in%20on%20the%20American%20Express%20laundry%20at%20Khetwadi%20and%20located%20its%20proprietor%20Shenolikar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20promptly%20told%20the%20PSIs%20Goud%20and%20Dudhat%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98AI%20SBH%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98AI%20Z%E2%80%99%20laundry%20marks%20belonged%20to%20his%20laundry%2C%20and%20the%20two%20male%20customers%20whom%20they%20belonged%20to%20stayed%20in%20the%20same%20locality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20arrests%3A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOn%20the%20same%20evening%2C%20the%20two%20accused%20Sayed%20Bakar%20Hussain%20and%20Sayed%20Ali%20Asad%20were%20arrested%20at%20Khetwadi%20back%20road.%20The%20two%20confessed%20to%20having%20committed%20the%20crime%20for%20pecuniary%20gain.%20They%20had%20stolen%20cash%2C%20gold%20and%20pearl%20ornaments%20and%20wrist%20watches%20worth%20Rs%2010%2C000.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fb2jZQOQMCr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fb2jZQOQMCr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dhaval%20Kulkarni%20(%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A3%E0%A5%80)%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40dhavalkulkarni)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdhavalkulkarni%2Fstatus%2F1745164543339474952%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dhaval%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20had%20stolen%20cash%2C%20gold%20and%20pearl%20ornaments%2C%20and%20wristwatches%20worth%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20Their%20fingerprints%20tallied%20with%20the%20chance%20prints%20found%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crime.%20They%20had%20discarded%20the%20blood-stained%20clothes%20and%20worn%20the%20washed%20clothes%20of%20Mr%20Choonawala.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20any%20crime%2C%20however%2C%20the%20police%20need%20to%20establish%20a%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Hussain%20was%20Choonawala%E2%80%99s%20driver%20and%20had%20been%20fired%20from%20his%20position.%20Hussain%20believed%20that%20Choonawala%20still%20owed%20him%20dues%20for%20working%20overtime%2C%20etc.%20Choonawala%20argued%20that%20all%20dues%20had%20been%20settled.%20During%20this%20argument%2C%20Hussain%E2%80%99s%20cousin%20Asad%20was%20also%20present.%20The%20argument%20with%20Choonawala%20escalated%20and%20soon%20the%20cousins%20committed%20the%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5Bcousins%5D%20later%20cut%20the%20%3Cem%3Edhobi%3C%2Fem%3E%20mark%20from%20their%20blood-stained%20clothes%20to%20disguise%20their%20identity%2C%20set%20fire%20to%20clothes%2C%20newspapers%2C%20etc%2C%20and%20opened%20the%20gas%20connection%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dhaval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20crimes%2C%20Hussain%20and%20Asad%20were%20sentenced%20to%20death%20by%20a%20principal%20sessions%20judge%20on%204%20November%201968.%20In%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%2C%20the%20police%20had%20nabbed%20the%20culprits%20and%20a%20court%20found%20them%20guilty%20and%20sentenced%20them.%20This%20remarkable%20quadruple%20murder%20case%20was%20among%20the%20last%20cases%20of%20DCP%20Vaidyanath%20Sami%E2%80%99s%20illustrious%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20587px)%20100vw%2C%20587px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FFingerprint-PNG-1705587151.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22587%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Murder%20case%20fingerprints%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FFingerprint-PNG-1705587151.jpg%20587w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FFingerprint-PNG-1705587151