ous%20generations%20grew%20up%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20an%20exciting%20future%20where%20If%20you%20worked%20hard%20and%20built%20a%20career%2C%20%5Bthe%20expectation%20was%20that%5D%20the%20future%20would%20be%20great.%20But%20our%20generation%20grew%20up%20with%20the%20reality%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20animal%20extinction%2C%20and%20severe%20air%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F201010%2Findia-water-pollution-cleaning-complaints-robot-hair-innovation-hair-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20pollution%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20I%20was%20about%20six%20years%20old%20and%20learned%20about%20these%20things%20on%20National%20Geographic%2C%20this%20discomfort%20about%20a%20bleak%20future%20has%20stayed%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Angad%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolving%20real-world%20problems%20has%20always%20excited%20him.%20A%20child%20prodigy%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20Angad%20built%20his%20first%20robot%20and%20a%20solar-powered%20boat%20at%20age%208%2C%20besides%20building%20a%20homegrown%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303783%2Fchennai-startup-avay-biosciences-builds-bio-3d-printer-to-print-human-tissues%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3D%20printer%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%2013%20and%20an%20e-reader%20(Virtual%20Brailler)%20for%20the%20visually-challenged%20by%2015.%20He%20briefly%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20schooling%20system%20because%20of%20his%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20rote%20learning-based%20state%20board%20system.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20school%20confusing.%20While%20I%20was%20doing%20well%20academically%2C%20the%20rote-based%20education%20didn%E2%80%99t%20build%20my%20fundamentals%20which%20would%20become%20obvious%20when%20I%E2%80%99d%20compete%20in%20Olympiads%20and